topic&index=18>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Wizards...........screw you And VI to</span><hr size=1> Ever try to use an AoE in a group? you get threatend to be booted. everyone has a false fear that AoE = certain death.<br>
